{"tid":1656602,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武對美心/福建幫行動升級，裝修與獅鳥同步進行","createTime":"2019-10-15T16:16:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T16:33:59.000Z","uid":276872,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"45c182ef1f65f0ab01aa523bcbb2bb71a00c5cd4","tid":1656602,"uid":276872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T16:16:12.000Z","msg":"個人認為一直裝修美心/福建幫公司成效不大，全因為仲有<span style=\"color: navy;\">藍絲</span>幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。下一次，勇武以突襲式裝修，毫無預告下(即係非周末)裝修店舖，同時獅鳥所有客人，以嚴懲佢哋仲幫襯。<span style=\"color: red;\">反正格殺勿論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<span style=\"color: red;\">[裝修]</span>美心/福建幫公司要為言行負責，<span style=\"color: red;\">[獅鳥]</span>客人要為錯誤消費決定負責</span>，一律抵L死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。等班客以後仲點敢幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，當買個教訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fee840b49f4bdd26bf1e14d82835c8ec24d3289b","tid":1656602,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T16:16:23.000Z","msg":"「突發」大量民陣1020九龍大遊行文宣流出<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1655703\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1655703</a>"},{"pid":"04632eb22a79b126b69eb79e0c2cf3880c1683f7","tid":1656602,"uid":276872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T16:17:01.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"3b21e9df1753155d6e3d83ae3432167113edf02c","tid":1656602,"uid":276872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T16:17:20.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"792524193f18d8424fcb596eef5964faca039c21","tid":1656602,"uid":276872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T16:17:35